      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and some fading in the clear coat, while the interior shows significant wear on the upholstery and carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it may require some upcoming maintenance like new brakes and a suspension refresh to return it to peak performance. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
