    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute showstopper! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and truly feels like it just left the factory. From its flawless exterior to its spotless interior, every detail has been meticulously cared for, ensuring a driving experience that is as smooth as it is luxurious. If you're looking for a top-tier vehicle that looks and performs like new, this is the one for you!",
