    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a wonderful example of pride in ownership, offering a reliable and polished driving experience. The exterior paint retains a beautiful depth and luster, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the seats are supportive and well-cared for, and every feature\u2014from the climate control to the premium sound system\u2014operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in great shape, having benefited from a strict regimen of scheduled maintenance and professional inspections. It drives with a smooth, confident grace, providing a quiet cabin and responsive handling that makes every commute a pleasure. This is a solid, honest car that is fully prepared for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
